            <li><a href="https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy" target="_blank">Firebase Analytics</a></li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Permissions</h2>
        <p>The Application may request the following permissions:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Internet:</strong> To stream audio content from our servers.</li>
            <li><strong>Storage/Media:</strong> To download and save audio files for offline listening.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
        <p>We do not store any user data on our servers. Any downloaded content or app settings are stored locally on your device and can be cleared by deleting the App's data or uninstalling the Application.</p>

        <h2>5. Children’s Privacy</h2>
        <p>The Application does not address anyone under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children.</p>

